title: Transmit 3.6.7+Serial Number.zip
description:
Product Description:

Take Transmit, our long standing, very Mac-like FTP / SFTP client. Then, add a ton of new features, including column view, tabs, a sidebar, new favorites, search, dock status, spring loaded folders, iDisk and WebDAV support, and much more.
The end result? We think it's the ultimate Mac FTP client, with more innovative features than anywhere else, and it makes FTP as simple, easy, and fun as, well, the Mac!
What's new in this version:

    * Re-worked preview drawer to avoid unnecessary file transfers and cancels, thus avoiding possible transfer stalls
    * Fixed a possible crash when changing selection quickly and right-clicking
    * Fixed several Dutch preference captions so they are no longer being truncated
    * Fixed S3 uploads with files greater than 2 GB
    * Fixed S3 problem when copying European bucket URL's
    * Fixed a problem in which files may be deleted when moving them into a subfolder
    * Improved S3 copied URLs when connecting to the EU S3 server
